Definition: very short-stemmed plant with thick leaves with soothing mucilaginous juice
Example: leaves develop spiny margins with maturity; native to Mediterranean region; grown widely in tropics and as houseplants
Synonyms: Aloe_vera, aloe, very, short-stemmed, plant, with, thick, leaves, soothing, mucilaginous, juice, develop, spiny, margins, maturity, native, to, Mediterranean, region, grown, widely, in, tropics, and, as, houseplants
Category: noun.plant
